      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/ecb155/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2017-05-08T20:46:48.606Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Vlonjato, nigjo; kur thua si Del-ta ; Kushtonin 1-2 e , pa e percaktuar mire monedhen, dhe me nje diference 100% , se 1 me 2 i thone 100% rritje te vleres, sikur me thone qe; Kushtonin 1400-2800 leke, gje qe stonon. Se mund te pranohet, qe; Kushtonin 1400-1500 leke, ose 1-1,2 euro, por jo 1-2 euro, 1400-2800 leke. Sikur nuk ka sens.</p>",
